objects.description: [Magic Hound](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0059) malware is capable of keylogging.(Citation: Unit 42 Magic Hound Feb 2017) [Magic Hound](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0059) used CWoolger and MPK, custom-developed malware, which recorded all keystrokes on an infected system.(Citation: Check Point Rocket Kitten)
